{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Do you know"},{"time":2000,"text":"that we have 1.4 million cellular radio masts"},{"time":5000,"text":"deployed worldwide?"},{"time":7000,"text":"And these are base stations."},{"time":9000,"text":"And we also have"},{"time":11000,"text":"more than five billion"},{"time":13000,"text":"of these devices here."},{"time":15000,"text":"These are cellular mobile phones."},{"time":18000,"text":"And with these mobile phones,"},{"time":20000,"text":"we transmit more than 600 terabytes of data"},{"time":22000,"text":"every month."},{"time":24000,"text":"This is a 6 with 14 zeroes --"},{"time":26000,"text":"a very large number."},{"time":28000,"text":"And wireless communications"},{"time":31000,"text":"has become a utility"},{"time":34000,"text":"like electricity and water."},{"time":36000,"text":"We use it everyday. We use it in our everyday lives now --"},{"time":39000,"text":"in our private lives, in our business lives."},{"time":41000,"text":"And we even have to be asked sometimes, very kindly,"},{"time":45000,"text":"to switch off the mobile phone at events like this"},{"time":47000,"text":"for good reasons."},{"time":50000,"text":"And it's this importance"},{"time":52000,"text":"why I decided to look into the issues"},{"time":54000,"text":"that this technology has,"},{"time":56000,"text":"because it's so fundamental to our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59000,"text":"And one of the issues is capacity."},{"time":61000,"text":"The way we transmit wireless data is by using electromagnetic waves --"},{"time":64000,"text":"in particular, radio waves."},{"time":67000,"text":"And radio waves are limited."},{"time":69000,"text":"They are scarce; they are expensive;"},{"time":71000,"text":"and we only have a certain range of it."},{"time":75000,"text":"And it's this limitation"},{"time":77000,"text":"that doesn't cope"},{"time":79000,"text":"with the demand of wireless data transmissions"},{"time":81000,"text":"and the number of bytes and data which are transmitted every month."},{"time":84000,"text":"And we are simply running out of spectrum."},{"time":86000,"text":"There's another problem."},{"time":88000,"text":"That is efficiency."},{"time":90000,"text":"These 1.4 million cellular radio masts, or base stations,"},{"time":93000,"text":"consume a lot of energy."},{"time":95000,"text":"And mind you, most of the energy"},{"time":97000,"text":"is not used to transmit the radio waves,"},{"time":99000,"text":"it is used to cool the base stations."},{"time":102000,"text":"Then the efficiency of such a base station"},{"time":104000,"text":"is only at about five percent."},{"time":107000,"text":"And that creates a big problem."},{"time":110000,"text":"Then there's another issue that you're all aware of."},{"time":113000,"text":"You have to switch off your mobile phone"},{"time":115000,"text":"during flights."},{"time":117000,"text":"In hospitals, they are security issues."},{"time":120000,"text":"And security is another issue."},{"time":123000,"text":"These radio waves penetrate through walls."},{"time":125000,"text":"They can be intercepted,"},{"time":127000,"text":"and somebody can make use of your network"},{"time":130000,"text":"if he has bad intentions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"So these are the main four issues."},{"time":134000,"text":"But on the other hand,"},{"time":136000,"text":"we have 14 billion of these:"},{"time":138000,"text":"light bulbs, light."},{"time":141000,"text":"And light is part of the electromagnetic spectrum."},{"time":144000,"text":"So let's look at this in the context"},{"time":146000,"text":"of the entire electromagnetic spectrum, where we have gamma rays."},{"time":149000,"text":"You don't want to get close to gamma rays, it could be dangerous."},{"time":151000,"text":"X-rays, useful when you go to hospitals."},{"time":154000,"text":"Then there's ultraviolet light."},{"time":156000,"text":"it's good for a nice suntan,"},{"time":158000,"text":"but otherwise dangerous for the human body."},{"time":160000,"text":"Infrared --"},{"time":162000,"text":"due to eye safety regulations,"},{"time":164000,"text":"can be only used with low power."},{"time":166000,"text":"And then we have the radio waves, they have the issues I've just mentioned."},{"time":169000,"text":"And in the middle there, we have this visible light spectrum."},{"time":172000,"text":"It's light,"},{"time":174000,"text":"and light has been around for many millions of years."},{"time":176000,"text":"And in fact, it has created us,"},{"time":179000,"text":"has created life,"},{"time":181000,"text":"has created all the stuff of life."},{"time":183000,"text":"So it's inherently safe to use."},{"time":186000,"text":"And wouldn't it be great to use that for wireless communications?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"Not only that, I compared [it to] the entire spectrum."},{"time":193000,"text":"I compared the radio waves spectrum --"},{"time":195000,"text":"the size of it --"},{"time":197000,"text":"with the size of the visible light spectrum."},{"time":199000,"text":"And guess what?"},{"time":201000,"text":"We have 10,000 times more of that spectrum,"},{"time":204000,"text":"which is there for us to use."},{"time":207000,"text":"So not only do we have this huge amount of spectrum,"},{"time":210000,"text":"let's compare that with a number I've just mentioned."},{"time":212000,"text":"We have 1.4 million"},{"time":214000,"text":"expensively deployed,"},{"time":216000,"text":"inefficient radio cellular base stations."},{"time":219000,"text":"And multiply that by 10,000,"},{"time":221000,"text":"then you end up at 14 billion."},{"time":223000,"text":"14 billion is the number of light bulbs installed already."},{"time":226000,"text":"So we have the infrastructure there."},{"time":228000,"text":"Look at the ceiling, you see all these light bulbs."},{"time":231000,"text":"Go to the main floor, you see these light bulbs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"Can we use them for communications?"},{"time":235000,"text":"Yes."},{"time":237000,"text":"What do we need to do?"},{"time":239000,"text":"The one thing we need to do"},{"time":241000,"text":"is we have to replace these inefficient incandescent light bulbs,"},{"time":244000,"text":"florescent lights,"},{"time":247000,"text":"with this new technology of LED,"},{"time":249000,"text":"LED light bulbs."},{"time":251000,"text":"An LED is a semiconductor. It's an electronic device."},{"time":253000,"text":"And it has a very nice acute property."},{"time":257000,"text":"Its intensity can be modulated"},{"time":260000,"text":"at very high speeds,"},{"time":262000,"text":"and it can be switched off at very high speeds."},{"time":265000,"text":"And this is a fundamental basic property"},{"time":267000,"text":"that we exploit"},{"time":269000,"text":"with our technology."},{"time":272000,"text":"So let's show how we do that."},{"time":274000,"text":"Let's go to the closest neighbor to the visible light spectrum --"},{"time":276000,"text":"go to remote controls."},{"time":278000,"text":"You all know remote controls have an infrared LED --"},{"time":280000,"text":"basically you switch on the LED, and if it's off, you switch it off."},{"time":283000,"text":"And it creates a simple, low-speed data stream"},{"time":286000,"text":"in 10,000 bits per second,"},{"time":288000,"text":"20,000 bits per second."},{"time":290000,"text":"Not usable for a YouTube video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"What we have done"},{"time":294000,"text":"is we have developed a technology"},{"time":297000,"text":"with which we can furthermore"},{"time":300000,"text":"replace the remote control of our light bulb."},{"time":302000,"text":"We transmit with our technology,"},{"time":304000,"text":"not only a single data stream,"},{"time":306000,"text":"we transmit thousands of data streams"},{"time":308000,"text":"in parallel,"},{"time":310000,"text":"at even higher speeds."},{"time":312000,"text":"And the technology we have developed --"},{"time":314000,"text":"it's called SIM OFDM."},{"time":316000,"text":"And it's spacial modulation --"},{"time":318000,"text":"these are the only technical terms, I'm not going into details --"},{"time":321000,"text":"but this is how we enabled"},{"time":323000,"text":"that light source"},{"time":325000,"text":"to transmit data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"You will say, \"Okay, this is nice --"},{"time":331000,"text":"a slide created in 10 minutes.\""},{"time":333000,"text":"But not only that."},{"time":335000,"text":"What we've done"},{"time":337000,"text":"is we have also developed a demonstrator."},{"time":340000,"text":"And I'm showing for the first time in public"},{"time":342000,"text":"this visible light demonstrator."},{"time":344000,"text":"And what we have here"},{"time":346000,"text":"is no ordinary desk lamp."},{"time":349000,"text":"We fit in an LED light bulb,"},{"time":351000,"text":"worth three U.S. dollars,"},{"time":354000,"text":"put in our signal processing technology."},{"time":356000,"text":"And then what we have here is a little hole."},{"time":359000,"text":"And the light goes through that hole."},{"time":361000,"text":"There's a receiver."},{"time":363000,"text":"The receiver will convert these little, subtle changes in the amplitude"},{"time":366000,"text":"that we create there"},{"time":368000,"text":"into an electrical signal."},{"time":370000,"text":"And that signal is then converted back"},{"time":372000,"text":"to a high-speed data stream."},{"time":374000,"text":"In the future we hope"},{"time":376000,"text":"that we can integrate this little hole"},{"time":378000,"text":"into these smart phones."},{"time":381000,"text":"And not only integrate a photo detector here,"},{"time":384000,"text":"but maybe use the camera inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388000,"text":"So what happens"},{"time":390000,"text":"when I switch on that light?"},{"time":395000,"text":"As you would expect,"},{"time":397000,"text":"it's a light, a desk lamp."},{"time":399000,"text":"Put your book beneath it and you can read."},{"time":402000,"text":"It's illuminating the space."},{"time":404000,"text":"But at the same time, you see this video coming up here."},{"time":408000,"text":"And that's a video, a high-definition video"},{"time":411000,"text":"that is transmitted through that light beam."},{"time":413000,"text":"You're critical."},{"time":415000,"text":"You think, \"Ha, ha, ha."},{"time":417000,"text":"This is a smart academic doing a little bit of tricks here.\""},{"time":420000,"text":"But let me do this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429000,"text":"Once again."},{"time":432000,"text":"Still don't believe?"},{"time":435000,"text":"It is this light"},{"time":437000,"text":"that transmits this high-definition video in a split stream."},{"time":441000,"text":"And if you look at the light,"},{"time":444000,"text":"it is illuminating as you would expect."},{"time":446000,"text":"You don't notice with your human eye."},{"time":448000,"text":"You don't notice the subtle changes in the amplitude"},{"time":451000,"text":"that we impress onto this light bulb."},{"time":454000,"text":"It's serving the purpose of illumination,"},{"time":456000,"text":"but at the same time, we are able to transmit this data."},{"time":459000,"text":"And you see,"},{"time":461000,"text":"even light from the ceiling comes down here to the receiver."},{"time":464000,"text":"It can ignore that constant light,"},{"time":467000,"text":"because all the receiver's interested in"},{"time":469000,"text":"are subtle changes."},{"time":474000,"text":"You also have a critical question now, and"},{"time":476000,"text":"you say, \"Okay,"},{"time":478000,"text":"do I have to have the light on all the time"},{"time":480000,"text":"to have this working?\""},{"time":482000,"text":"And the answer is yes."},{"time":484000,"text":"But, you can dim down the light"},{"time":488000,"text":"to a level that it appears to be off."},{"time":490000,"text":"And you are still able to transmit data -- that's possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"So I've mentioned to you the four challenges."},{"time":496000,"text":"Capacity:"},{"time":498000,"text":"We have 10,000 times more spectrum,"},{"time":500000,"text":"10,000 times more LEDs"},{"time":502000,"text":"installed already in the infrastructure there."},{"time":504000,"text":"You would agree with me, hopefully,"},{"time":506000,"text":"there's no issue of capacity anymore."},{"time":508000,"text":"Efficiency:"},{"time":510000,"text":"This is data through illumination --"},{"time":512000,"text":"it's first of all an illumination device."},{"time":514000,"text":"And if you do the energy budget,"},{"time":517000,"text":"the data transmission comes for free --"},{"time":519000,"text":"highly energy efficient."},{"time":521000,"text":"I don't mention the high energy efficiency"},{"time":523000,"text":"of these LED light bulbs."},{"time":525000,"text":"If the whole world would deploy them,"},{"time":527000,"text":"you would save hundreds of power plants."},{"time":530000,"text":"That's aside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"And then I've mentioned the availability."},{"time":534000,"text":"You will agree with me that we have lights in the hospital."},{"time":537000,"text":"You need to see what to do."},{"time":539000,"text":"You have lights in an aircraft."},{"time":541000,"text":"So it's everywhere in a day there is light."},{"time":543000,"text":"Look around. Everywhere. Look at your smart phone."},{"time":546000,"text":"It has a flashlight, an LED flashlight."},{"time":548000,"text":"These are potential sources for high-speed data transmission."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"And then there's security."},{"time":555000,"text":"You would agree with me"},{"time":557000,"text":"that light doesn't penetrate through walls."},{"time":560000,"text":"So no one, if I have a light here,"},{"time":562000,"text":"if I have secure data,"},{"time":564000,"text":"no one on the other side of this room through that wall"},{"time":566000,"text":"would be able to read that data."},{"time":568000,"text":"And there's only data where there is light."},{"time":571000,"text":"So if I don't want that receiver to receive the data,"},{"time":575000,"text":"then what I could do,"},{"time":579000,"text":"turn it away."},{"time":582000,"text":"So the data goes in that direction, not there anymore."},{"time":584000,"text":"Now we can in fact see where the data is going to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"So for me,"},{"time":593000,"text":"the applications of it,"},{"time":596000,"text":"to me, are beyond imagination at the moment."},{"time":600000,"text":"We have had a century of very nice, smart application developers."},{"time":604000,"text":"And you only have to notice, where we have light,"},{"time":607000,"text":"there is a potential way to transmit data."},{"time":610000,"text":"But I can give you a few examples."},{"time":613000,"text":"Well you may see the impact already now."},{"time":617000,"text":"This is a remote operated vehicle"},{"time":619000,"text":"beneath the ocean."},{"time":621000,"text":"And they use light to illuminate space down there."},{"time":624000,"text":"And this light can be used to transmit wireless data"},{"time":626000,"text":"that these things [use] to communicate with each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":629000,"text":"Intrinsically safe environments"},{"time":631000,"text":"like this petrochemical plant --"},{"time":633000,"text":"you can't use RF, it may generate antenna sparks,"},{"time":636000,"text":"but you can use light -- you see plenty of light there."},{"time":639000,"text":"In hospitals,"},{"time":641000,"text":"for new medical instruments;"},{"time":644000,"text":"in streets for traffic control."},{"time":647000,"text":"Cars have LED-based headlights, LED-based back lights,"},{"time":650000,"text":"and cars can communicate with each other"},{"time":652000,"text":"and prevent accidents"},{"time":655000,"text":"in the way that they exchange information."},{"time":658000,"text":"Traffic lights can communicate to the car and so on."},{"time":661000,"text":"And then you have these millions of street lamps"},{"time":664000,"text":"deployed around the world."},{"time":667000,"text":"And every street lamp could be a free access point."},{"time":669000,"text":"We call it, in fact, a Li-Fi,"},{"time":671000,"text":"light-fidelity."},{"time":673000,"text":"And then we have these aircraft cabins."},{"time":677000,"text":"There are hundreds of lights in an aircraft cabin,"},{"time":681000,"text":"and each of these lights"},{"time":683000,"text":"could be a potential transmitter of wireless data."},{"time":686000,"text":"So you could enjoy your most favorite TED video"},{"time":689000,"text":"on your long flight back home."},{"time":691000,"text":"Online life. So that is a vision, I think, that is possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":700000,"text":"So, all we would need to do"},{"time":702000,"text":"is to fit a small microchip"},{"time":704000,"text":"to every potential illumination device."},{"time":707000,"text":"And this would then combine"},{"time":710000,"text":"two basic functionalities:"},{"time":712000,"text":"illumination and wireless data transmission."},{"time":714000,"text":"And it's this symbiosis that I personally believe"},{"time":717000,"text":"could solve the four essential problems"},{"time":719000,"text":"that face us in wireless communication these days."},{"time":722000,"text":"And in the future,"},{"time":724000,"text":"you would not only have 14 billion light bulbs,"},{"time":727000,"text":"you may have 14 billion Li-Fis"},{"time":730000,"text":"deployed worldwide --"},{"time":732000,"text":"for a cleaner, a greener,"},{"time":734000,"text":"and even a brighter future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}